Divisional titles on leaves )o(4 and G2 respectively: "Deo ter opt. max. moderatori vigilantissimo suas vigilias C.C. rhetores Salisburgenses. anno MDCLXXXI"; "Deo ter opt. max. motori primo tranquillissimo sua somnia D.D. poëtae Salisburgenses. anno MDCLXXXI." Registration is continuous despite foliation. Numbered leaves with engraved circular emblems on recto and blank versos.
